Many people were left in a state of panic yesterday after a final year student of Rivers State University was shot dead by rival cultists inside campus. The yet to be identified victim, it was gathered was shot in the stomach. Students were seen rushing to the scene as he laid on the floor before being rushed into a car. Watch video below: Graphic: River State University finalist gunned down by rival cultists on campus A post shared by  Instablog9ja (@instablog9ja) on Jul 29, 2019 at 11:12am PDT Source